<!--
    File: coverage_dashboard.html.in
    Description: This file serves as a modern, responsive dashboard for viewing code coverage reports.
                 It is designed to be generated by a build system (e.g., CMake) where project-specific
                 variables such as PROJECT_NAME and COVERAGE_DATA_JSON are injected.
                 The dashboard renders a list of coverage modules as interactive cards, allowing users
                 to view detailed HTML reports or download raw .lcov data files.
    
    Author: Mohammad Raziei
    Email: mohammadraziei1375@gmail.com
    GitHub: https://github.com/mohammadraziei
    
